<note n="0837003" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0837003">迦攝波＝迦葉波【三】【宮】下同</note>
<note n="0837004" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0837004">彼＝若【三】【宮】【聖乙】</note>
<note n="0837005" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0837005">興＝與【明】</note>
<note n="0837006" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0837006">摩揭陀＝摩竭陀【明】</note>
<note n="0837007" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0837007">煖＝暖【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0837008" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0837008">〔之〕－【聖】【聖乙】</note>
<note n="0838001" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0838001">披＝被【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0838002" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0838002">健＝犍【三】【宮】＊</note>
<note n="0838003" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0838003">椎＝稚【宋】【元】【宮】【聖乙】＊</note>
<note n="0838004" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0838004">（事）＋聞【聖乙】</note>
<note n="0838005" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0838005">此下聖本有光明皇后願文</note>
